sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Ingress as Platform Ingress<br/>(Gateway API / Istio)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3
    participant Server as AutoGluon Server Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP, 8081/TCP gRPC
    participant Storage as Cloud Storage<br/>(S3/GCS/Azure/HF)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KServeCtrl as KServe Controller
    participant FS as Local Filesystem

    Note over KServeCtrl,Server: Flow 1: Pod Lifecycle & Model Loading

    KServeCtrl->>Server: Create Pod (InferenceService CR)<br/>K8s API / mTLS / ServiceAccount

    Note over Server: runtime_paths.py: Set writable CWD<br/>(non-root container UID 1001)

    Server->>Storage: Storage.download() -- model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / GCP SA / Azure / Bearer
    Storage-->>Server: Model artifacts (tar.gz / directory)
    Server->>FS: Write model to local path

    Note over Server: Auto-Detection Sequence

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over Server: predictor_detect.py
        Server->>Server: version_compat.py: Check model version<br/>(allow patch mismatch, reject major/minor)
        Server->>Server: Try TimeSeriesPredictor.load()
        alt TimeSeries model detected
            Server->>Server: Return AutoGluonDetectedModel(TS)
        else TimeSeries load fails
            Server->>Server: Try TabularPredictor.load()
            Server->>Server: Return AutoGluonDetectedModel(Tabular)
        end
    end

    Note over Server: Model loaded, server ready

    Note over Client,Server: Flow 2: v1 REST Inference (Tabular + TimeSeries)

    Client->>Ingress: POST /v1/models/{name}:predict<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.3<br/>Auth: Platform auth (Bearer)
    Ingress->>Server: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8080 (cluster internal, no TLS)
    alt Tabular Model
        Server->>Server: TabularPredictor.predict(DataFrame)<br/>or predict_proba (if PREDICT_PROBA=true)
    else TimeSeries Model
        Server->>Server: TimeSeriesPredictor.predict()<br/>Map columns via predictor_metadata.json
    end
    Server-->>Ingress: JSON prediction response
    Ingress-->>Client: HTTPS response

    Note over Client,Server: Flow 3: v2 REST Inference (Tabular Only)

    Client->>Ingress: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.3
    Ingress->>Server: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8080
    Server->>Server: Decode v2 tensor inputs → DataFrame<br/>Map v2 datatypes ↔ AutoGluon features
    Server->>Server: TabularPredictor.predict(DataFrame)
    Server-->>Ingress: v2 InferResponse (tensor outputs)
    Ingress-->>Client: HTTPS response

    Note over Client,Server: Flow 4: gRPC Inference (v2 Protocol)

    Client->>Ingress: gRPC ModelInfer<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.3
    Ingress->>Server: Forward request<br/>gRPC/8081
    Server->>Server: Process inference via GRPCInferenceService
    Server-->>Ingress: gRPC InferResponse
    Ingress-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over Client,Server: Health & Metadata

    Client->>Ingress: GET /v2/health/ready
    Ingress->>Server: HTTP/8080
    Server-->>Ingress: 200 OK (model loaded)
    Ingress-->>Client: Health status
